(PROBECONFIG)
(Description: Probe Configuration File)
(Initial Coding 1/25/2024: Joshua Smith)
(macro to setup probe specs and units, called by every macro)

(important local variables)
@100 = R_SYS_INFO[0,2]           (TOOL NUMBER)
@101 = R_TOOL_DATA[0,@100,3]     (TOOL DIAMETER)
@102 = @101/2                    (TOOL RADIUS)
@103 = 100                       (FEED SPEED in/m, change to match your unit of choice, for metric users start at 2540mm))
@104 = 50                        (FAST PROBE SPEED in/m, change to match your unit of choice, for metric users start at 1270mm)
@105 = 2.5                       (SLOW PROBE SPEED in/m, change to match your unit of choice, for metric users start at 63mm)
@106 = .5                        (WEB PROBE DISTANCE in, change to match your unit of choice, for metric users start at 6mm)
@107 = [R_TOOL_DATA[0,@100,203]] (TOOL LENGHT OFFSET)
@108 = .25                       (PROBE BACKOFF DISTANCE,change to match your unit of choice, for metric users start at 6mm)

G90

M99